          * `heavy_armor` - Heavy Armor
          * `robe` - Robe
          * `melee_one_hand` - One-Handed Melee
          * `melee_two_hand` - Two-Handed Melee
          * `ranged` - Ranged
          * `thrown` - Thrown
          * `shield` - Shield
          * `jewelry` - Jewelry
          * `clothing` - Clothing
          * `other` - Other
